{"tid":2325790,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"部電腦最近好多奇怪問題，跪求","createTime":"2020-12-15T00:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T06:52:01.000Z","uid":194876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"92ca9925ebbf98efe69d76496ddc653b8cb6c792","tid":2325790,"uid":194876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T00:56:02.000Z","msg":"部腦都砌左5年幾<br />\n最近幾個月有好多問題<br />\n     有時開機後一陣部腦會無啦啦輕機卡住，然後有電流聲，幾秒後就會自動重開機，唔熄機既話就唔會再輕第2次。 <br />\n     有時會開機會卡住bios位，等好耐入到win啦，就會認唔到ssd/hhd<br />\n     鍵盤隨機總有1-2粒制㩒唔到，過1日又㩒得番<br />\n     個喇叭低音箱有時會冇左重音，要機箱尾抆線再插過先得，但一搞機箱後面dusb/3.5mm 線通常會斷上網，甚至輕機自動重開<br />\n     有時開機無畫面，會重插gpu ram ssd/hhd 上面問題就會好番，但過一排又有問題<br />\n洗過機都係咁，究竟部腦咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237b2cbab4ac82d38a5b1dee7ed29bbd75d50438","tid":2325790,"uid":145987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T01:00:55.000Z","msg":"拆出黎洗"},{"pid":"185be0490d49201286ab3b90a1c45c7d4c795672","tid":2325790,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T02:21:17.000Z","msg":"底板<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾耐冇清塵"},{"pid":"6fe52afddfb2bab70f8b7c80c0977a195c36c604","tid":2325790,"uid":194876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"185be0490d49201286ab3b90a1c45c7d4c795672","tid":2325790,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T02:21:17.000Z","msg":"底板<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾耐冇清塵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T02:33:44.000Z","msg":"清過唔太多塵"},{"pid":"6002ebe364c80c4a6eff5f78233c3eef12e114dd","tid":2325790,"uid":270619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T06:52:01.000Z","msg":"ssd/hhd has issues"}]}